export default function LeftNav({ data }) { return (
{data && data.map((item, index) => (
Card Title

    Missions Name: {item.mission_name}

  • List Mission Ids: {item.mission_id}

Launch Year: {item.launch_year}

Successful Launch: {item.launch_success}

Successful Landing: {item.launch_success?.rocket?.first_stage?.cores[0] ?.land_success ? 'Yes' : 'No'}

))}
) }
